data.description: The Jackson II is a spacious four bedroom home with a guest suite on the main level. The two story foyer has a railed overlook above, and encompasses a stairway with a feature window over the landing. The family room and breakfast area overlook the rear year, and the centrally located kitchen is open to all main living areas of the home, for good traffic flow and entertaining. The upstairs primary bedroom features a trey ceiling and luxury bath with his and hers vanities, linen closet, enclosed commode, garden tub, and separate shower, adjacent to a large closet. Three additional bedrooms and a hall bath complete the upstairs. Lots of upgrades in this home!
